{"tid":2167302,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"休班狗偷拍水炮車裙底罪成 上訴被駁回 官：知法犯法 咎由自取","createTime":"2020-08-21T04:34:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-21T05:02:19.000Z","uid":321059,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"ebe90cfc30fa9d742f7bbbadf666c8c12f4af2da","tid":2167302,"uid":321059,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T04:34:59.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/society/偷拍-警嫂-罪成囚兩個月-休班警長上訴遭駁回-官-知法犯法-咎由自取/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%E5%81%B7%E6%8B%8D-%E8%AD%A6%E5%AB%82-%E7%BD%AA%E6%88%90%E5%9B%9A%E5%85%A9%E5%80%8B%E6%9C%88-%E4%BC%91%E7%8F%AD%E8%AD%A6%E9%95%B7%E4%B8%8A%E8%A8%B4%E9%81%AD%E9%A7%81%E5%9B%9E-%E5%AE%98-%E7%9F%A5%E6%B3%95%E7%8A%AF%E6%B3%95-%E5%92%8E%E7%94%B1%E8%87%AA%E5%8F%96%2F&d=fUB9jTkReJc3fMEQQRliuzcyzTZykTUlxRhnZlW9F%2Bg%3D&h=6c200451\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%E5%81%B7%E6%8B%8D-%E8%AD%A6%E5%AB%82-%E7%BD%AA%E6%88%90%E5%9B%9A%E5%85%A9%E5%80%8B%E6%9C%88-%E4%BC%91%E7%8F%AD%E8%AD%A6%E9%95%B7%E4%B8%8A%E8%A8%B4%E9%81%AD%E9%A7%81%E5%9B%9E-%E5%AE%98-%E7%9F%A5%E6%B3%95%E7%8A%AF%E6%B3%95-%E5%92%8E%E7%94%B1%E8%87%AA%E5%8F%96%2F&h=23bb05d9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/society/偷拍-警嫂-罪成囚兩個月-休班警長上訴遭駁回-官-知法犯法-咎由自取/</a><br />\n<br />\n一名休班警長被指於 2017 年於油塘大本型商場的扶手電梯，偷拍一名女子的裙底，不料對方為「警嫂」並當場揭發事件。休班警長其後被控一項作出有違公德行為罪，並遭裁定罪成，判囚兩個月。警長不服定罪及判刑，向高等法院提上訴，案件經聆訊後，高院法官黃崇厚今頒下判詞，指原審裁判官原則上無犯錯，刑期亦非明顯過重，駁回上訴，維持原判，警長須即時服刑。<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">法官於判詞中指不能忽視被告身為警務人員，知法犯法的情況，並認為他並非一時衝動或判斷失誤而犯案，面對懲罰是咎由自取。</span></span>"},{"pid":"d18053aae4ff8aa6fa797dc6e044adc107275746","tid":2167302,"uid":300782,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T04:36:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a3f04b2474e7ca5966d563de02fd9aab75c5710","tid":2167302,"uid":8014,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T04:37:51.000Z","msg":"扮藍屌個官好黃啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n只要係警察 就算販毒都唔可以判罪成<br />\n<br />\n否則就係煽動公眾仇恨警隊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a9495e366ed6118d855b810b2a9299fefc9c079","tid":2167302,"uid":25794,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"d18053aae4ff8aa6fa797dc6e044adc107275746","tid":2167302,"uid":300782,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T04:36:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T04:39:21.000Z","msg":"裙底襲警"},{"pid":"d55a563638f0d7d5ee82d7d07cb55e204afd6512","tid":2167302,"uid":6981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T04:46:18.000Z","msg":"揀中水炮車先中招姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"848f704b32c111fb5f05721756791bcc4a0efa89","tid":2167302,"uid":127929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T04:53:29.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">放監咪又係復職</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a60fcf0549a07889b9d64f9308f42338fef03148","tid":2167302,"uid":237425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d55a563638f0d7d5ee82d7d07cb55e204afd6512","tid":2167302,"uid":6981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T04:46:18.000Z","msg":"揀中水炮車先中招姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T04:56:08.000Z","msg":"都抵撚死<br />\n<br />\n仲有單狗車狗摑狗仔個單<br />\n唔知要唔要加監<br />\n<br />\n最好以後狗打狗<br />\n一齊死"},{"pid":"c9c340e7c7c1e621f924e75cc0e31e5bc987ef8d","tid":2167302,"uid":237425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sc